 Rai.svg|border|22px]] [[Kirat Autonomous State]]\n* Ethnic group: [[Kirati people|Kiratis]]\n* Proposed state: Kirat\n* Political party: [[Kirat Janabadi Workers Party]]\n\n[[File:Flagge fan Madesj.png|border|22px]] [[Madhesh]]\n* Ethnic group: [[Madhesi people]]s (including [[Maithils]], [[Bhojpuri people|Bhojpuris]] and [[Tharu people|Tharus]]).\n* Proposed state: Madhesh\n* Advocacy group: [[Alliance for Independent Madhesh]]<ref>{{cite news |title=Madhesis in Nepal to continue protests till next election, says separatist leader |url=http://www.catchnews.com/world-news/madhesis-in-nepal-to-continue-protests-till-next-election-says-separatist-leader-1454421767.html |accessdate=1 March 2016 |publisher=Catch News |date=3 February 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306051659/http://www.catchnews.com/world-news/madhesis-in-nepal-to-continue-protests-till-next-election-says-separatist-leader-1454421767.html |archive-date=6 March 2016 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n* Militant Group: [[Janatantrik Terai Mukti Morcha]], Madhesh Mukti Tigers (MMT), Tharuwan National Liberation Front (TNLF).<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.satp.org/satporgtp/countries/nepal/terroristoutfits/mao.html |title=Nepal Terrorist Groups \u2013 Madheshi Armed Outfits |website=satp.org |access-date=30 September 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170915021838/http://www.satp.org/satporgtp/countries/nepal/terroristoutfits/MAO.html |archive-date=15 September 2017 |url-status=live }}</ref>\n\n[[Terai]]\n* Ethnic group: [[Teraibasi people|Teraibasi]]\n* Proposed state: Terai\n* Political party: [[Terai Army]]\n\n== Pakistan ==\n{{Main|Secession in Pakistan|Separatist movements of Pakistan}}\n{{Further|Insurgency in Balochistan}}\n[[Azad Kashmir]]\n* Ethnic group: [[Kashmiris|Western Kashmiri]]\n* Proposed state: [[File:Jammu-Kashmir-flag.png|22px|border]] [[Azad Kashmir]]<ref>https://www.nytimes.com/2019/09/19/world/asia/pakistan-kashmir-independence.html</ref>\n* Advocacy group: [