an-rohingya-national-organisation.html#|archive-date=30 May 2016|url-status=live|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n\n[[File:Flag of the Shan State.svg|22px|border]] [[Shan States]]\n* Ethnic group: [[Shan people|Shan]] (member of the [[Unrepresented Nations and Peoples Organization]])\n** Proposed state: [[Federated Shan States|Shan Republic]] [[File:Flag of the Shan State.svg|22px|border]]\n** Political party: [[Shan Democratic Union]]\n** Militant organisation: [[Shan State Army]]\n** Advocacy group: [[Restoration Council of Shan State]]\n** Government in exile: Interim Government of Federated Shan States<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.tgte-us.org/mission.html |title=The Transnational Government of Tamil Eelam |website=tgte-us.org |access-date=20 September 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120921170550/http://www.tgte-us.org/mission.html |archive-date=21 September 2012 |url-status=dead |df=dmy-all }}</ref>\n\n[[File:Flag of the Wa State.png|22px|border]] [[Wa State]]\n* Ethnic group: [[Wa people|Wa]]\n** Proposed state: [[Wa State|Wa Democratic People's Republic]] [[File:Flag of the Wa State.png|22px|border]]\n** Political party: [[United Wa State Party]]\n** Militant organisation: [[United Wa State Army]]\n\n[[File:Flag of Bnei Menashe.svg|22px|border]] [[Zale'n-gam]]\n* Ethnic group: [[Kuki people|Kuki]]\n** Proposed state: [[Zale'n-gam]] [[File:Flag of Bnei Menashe.svg|22px|border]]\n** Militant organisation: [[Kuki National Army]]\n** Advocacy group: [[Kuki National Organisation]]\n\n[[File:Flag of Zomi Re-unification Organisation.svg|22px|border]] [[Zogam]]\n* Ethnic group: [[Zomi]]\n** Proposed state: [[Republic of Zogam]] or [[Federated State of Zomi]] [[File:Flag of Zomi Re-unification Organisation.svg|22px|border]]\n** Political parties: [[Zomi National Congress]], [[Zomi Reunification Organization]]\n** Militant organisations: [[Zomi National Front/Army]], [[Zomi Revolutionary Army]],\n** Advocacy group: [[Global Zomi Alliance]]\n** Government in exile: 